Use of SVG in html


1. Go to IcoMoon.io site to select the svg file that you want.

2. download the zip file (make sure that you deselct the PNG in setting of svg)

3. Copy the SVG folder and symbol-defs.svg (rename it to the sprite.svg/ or whatever you like) in project's img folder.

4. in html, we can use the SVG using following link.

5. Syntax :

			<svg>
			
				<use xlink:href="img/sprite.svg#icon-name"></use>
			
			</svg>
			
			
